Firstly to my American friends &ndash; I love you all, I love your country and I&rsquo;d like to be let back in again next week please. But honestly&hellip;
Canada, Oh Canada, Where The Air Is Sweet, The Dogs Don&rsquo;t Bite and They Actually Maintain The Roads.
